<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ب ع ث<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٦٧٤ - ب ع ث]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ابتعثَ يبتعث، ابتِعاثًا، فهو مُبتعِث، والمفعول مُبتعَث<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ابتعثَ الشَّخصَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - بعَثه، أرسله <span class="c1">"كان من المُبتَعَثين للدِّراسة"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - بعثَه، أيقظه من نومه <span class="c1">"أَتَانِي اللَّيْلَةَ آتِيَانِ فَابْتَعَثَانِي <span class="c4">[حديث]</span> "</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>